{"tw": {"3191580": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Harem Dungeon", "steam_appid": 3191580, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Idle Clicker with a Narrative Twist</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike traditional idle games, Harem Dungeon weaves narrative progression into its core mechanics. Even when you’re not actively playing, your party continues to battle and gather resources. When you return, dive back into the stories and continue your journey through the dungeon, saving new girls and uncovering their tales. It’s a gameplay experience that blends strategy, story, and idle mechanics in a way that keeps you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras/bd1f1b7c64ead8f040f9017607e5c9be.avif?t=1770719724\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras_big/bd1f1b7c64ead8f040f9017607e5c9be.avif?t=1770719724 width=800 height=458 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unveil the Stories of the Dungeon and Its Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harem Dungeon offers a unique blend of narrative and idle gameplay. As you progress through the dungeon, you'll uncover the stories behind each character you meet. The deeper you delve, the more intriguing the tales become. Every floor holds new revelations about the world and the enigmatic dungeon itself, enticing you to push further. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras/0c83ad593b0598f660ea356de402eb43.avif?t=1770719724\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras_big/0c83ad593b0598f660ea356de402eb43.avif?t=1770719724 width=800 height=438 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet New Girls and Expand Your Party</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your journey is filled with encounters with mysterious and captivating girls, each trapped deep within the dungeon. Every few floors, you'll rescue a new companion who will join your party. These girls aren’t just allies; they have rich backstories that unfold as you progress, adding layers of depth to your adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras/e2d30e453c661f0eefaa74a133a14e71.avif?t=1770719724\" width=576 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras/5f558b28855d7d5d7525d376721811d9.avif?t=1770719724\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras_big/5f558b28855d7d5d7525d376721811d9.avif?t=1770719724 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle Monsters and Descend into the Dungeon </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While Harem Dungeon is an idle clicker, the journey through the dungeon is far from idle. As you defeat waves of monsters and overcome challenges, you’ll unlock new levels and rescue more girls. The deeper you go, the tougher the enemies, but with every victory, your party grows stronger, and the narrative deepens.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras/f6b3a85ed5861042c7c0e65e5abb915b.avif?t=1770719724\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191580/extras_big/f6b3a85ed5861042c7c0e65e5abb915b.avif?t=1770719724 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cute Steam Achievement<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: